# cntrl_alt_lenny's local AI-agent workflow — kept off fork main so upstream
# PRs (cntrl-alt-lenny:<branch> → xbret:main) never carry it. Files stay
# on disk locally; the brain/decomper/scaffolder Claude Code sessions read
# them from there. Cross-machine sync (if/when needed) goes via a separate
# mechanism (sibling repo / syncthing / manual copy), not the fork.
/AGENTS.md
/CLAUDE.md
/.claude/
/docs/briefs/
/docs/state.md
/docs/decomp-workflow.md
